    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> salmon flakes</strong> and <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>to the bowl with the mashed potato</p><p>Add the <strong>lime zest</strong>, <strong>egg[s]</strong>, <strong>mango chutney</strong>, your<strong> allspice</strong>,<strong> </strong>your<strong> cayenne pepper </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> </strong>2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> [4 tbsp]</span><strong> flour</strong> and a very generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> fishcake mixture</strong></p>",
